# HighAsCG — paths omitted from the live USB squashfs (penguins-eggs / mksquashfs)
#
# Entries are relative to filesystem root (no leading slash).
# See docs/WO47_ISO_VS_EXFAT.md — minimal ISO shells vs payload on exFAT sim/highascg.
#
# --- Swap (not on operator USB; strip-host-swap-for-live-iso.sh also removes before produce) ---
swap.img
swapfile

