# --- Tailscale (omit node identity from cloned ISO) ---
# eggs `--clone` snapshots the build host. Whatever paths hold tailscaled state will make the
# live machine reuse the SAME tailnet node key as the builder ("steals" that node's slot).
#
# Default `.deb` (`tailscale.com/install.sh`): often `/var/lib/tailscale/` — but your host may
# show NO such directory if Tailscale is installed via snap or uses a custom `--statedir=` /
# `--state=` in `/etc/default/tailscaled` or the systemd unit drop-in.
#
# Snap installs keep writable state under `/var/snap/tailscale/…` (especially …/common/).
var/lib/tailscale
var/lib/tailscale/*
var/snap/tailscale
var/snap/tailscale/*
